{"tid":462325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［無面比］南韓安排川普會悟「慰安婦」致日本強烈不滿","createTime":"2017-11-08T12:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T16:57:13.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"556733f0da2b4e4f2330fe03d36b3ba06ffbbdc3","tid":462325,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"川普這趟亞洲行在南韓也有出人意料的舉動。昨（7）日在南韓總統府的安排下，曾經當過慰安婦的88歲婦女李容洙出席招待美國總統川普（Donald Trump）的晚宴。<br />\n日本《共同社》報導，日本內閣官房長官菅義偉在記者會上對南韓政府的作法表示強烈不滿，並指出此舉並不理智，在謀求日美韓三國加強合作以因應北韓威脅的過程中，需要避免會帶來不良影響的舉動。<br />\n出席晚宴的李容洙，是不接受2015年日韓政府協議的前慰安婦之一，她曾在晚宴上與川普輕輕擁抱並簡短打招呼。南韓青瓦臺表示，邀請前慰安婦出席晚宴，是基於有必要展現平衡觀點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/204658_faf64c2cc41fc74f035a1e8cf2a53a3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F204658_faf64c2cc41fc74f035a1e8cf2a53a3e.jpg&h=74c77477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓果然有種"},{"pid":"b20d58d9bfd572c4810eb2ce3cd7e05edb30f5ce","tid":462325,"uid":29804,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"文在寅打盟友就叻<br />\n對北韓就乜都唔敢"},{"pid":"94dc2c0e4e4ea11548dffb657cba7ae2904bab0b","tid":462325,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"啲左膠大敵當前都要玩呢啲咩女權平權自由公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62907785d8cf62df9ce307eb8784c56604958c71","tid":462325,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e077571346a56c4655c8107a257702fd448e55","tid":462325,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"打北韓就陽光 對日本就平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文在寅其實係咪韓奸？"},{"pid":"ff60d1f56178cdfc676592b0376a97ecce4a2a9e","tid":462325,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"cite